# .claudeignore — AI OS File Access Blacklist
# Claude Code cannot READ, MODIFY, or DELETE any path listed here.
# Think of this as a firewall: if it's here, Claude Code is blind to it.
#
# SCOPE: Applied to ALL Claude Code sessions operating in d:\Project\AI OS
# AUTHORITY: Tier 0 (Constitution) — cannot be overridden by any agent or task

# ============================================================
# TIER 0 — CONSTITUTION FILES (Absolute protection)
# No agent may modify these. Only Antigravity + explicit user approval.
# ============================================================
CLAUDE.md
gatekeeper.ps1
registry.json

# Primary location (v2) — REAL files
shared-context/SOUL.md
shared-context/AGENTS.md

# Legacy redirect stubs in rules/ — keep protected (read-only)
rules/AGENTS.md
rules/SOUL.md

# New Tier 1 governance files — protected from agent modification
shared-context/THESIS.md
shared-context/GOVERNANCE.md
rules/APPROVAL_GATES.md

# ============================================================
# TIER 1 — STRATEGY FILES (Protected)
# High-level thesis and roadmap. Read is OK, write is forbidden.
# ============================================================
shared-context/THESIS.md
shared-context/ROADMAP.md

# ============================================================
# CREDENTIAL & SENSITIVE DATA
# API keys, secrets — never expose to agent context
# ============================================================
*.env
.env*
**/secrets/**
**/keys/**

# Master secrets store
ops/secrets/

# Service config with hardcoded tokens
ops/scripts/config.json

# ============================================================
# GIT HISTORY — Never touch (use git CLI explicitly)
# ============================================================
.git/
**/.git/

# ============================================================
# ARCHIVE & BACKUP — Preserve as-is
# ============================================================
DATA/Archive/
**/backup/
**/*.backup

# ============================================================
# NODE & BUILD ARTIFACTS — Irrelevant bloat for context window
# ============================================================
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# ============================================================
# LOGS — Read-only territory (agents write to telemetry/ only)
# ============================================================
**/logs/
**/*.log
